{"tid":2406432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 頭先去親戚屋企 比個藍藍表弟串貢貢","createTime":"2021-02-13T07:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T15:40:49.000Z","uid":384104,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ff6fed87376095c481106e1500607b3474674a","tid":2406432,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"話說頭先同緊表親一家坐車去拜年<br />\n本身都知佢地藍 係<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">藍到發黑個隻</span></span><br />\n會去支持政府集會 又成日FB轉貼港人港地啲po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以自己同細佬都唔想一齊同車 不過見係新年先聚一下就算<br />\n點知頭先就嚟料 如下:<br />\n<br />\n我見到表弟係度掃下掃下咁 就走過去問佢<br />\n我: 表弟 喺度掃緊咩啊 係咪有小精靈捉啊?<br />\n藍藍表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咪掃緊個<span class=\"xx-large\">安心出行</span>囉 有幾好用 好多地方都有<br />\n我細細聱咁講咗句: <span class=\"small\">防疫撚 咪又係政府拎嚟做大數據 想trace 人</span><br />\n點知藍藍表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻起曬鋼: 係啊係啊 自由撚 咪就係你班小黃人成日<br />\n陰謀論咁睇政府 又話咩基因碼 又唔去接種 搞到疫情都仲係咁反覆囉<br />\n跟住仲講咗句<strong>藍絲界嘅名言</strong>: 就算政府係做大數據 你估你地啲基因 <br />\n咩信息定位好值錢啊<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">你地如果冇犯法嘅 驚咩啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住藍藍表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又繼續講: 你地班小黃黃如果真係唔驚嘅<br />\n又覺得政府嘅政策係唔合理嘅 好似咩限聚令 咩封小區<br />\n係會損害你地所謂嘅自由 做咩唔出嚟遊行 示威<br />\n反正你地班小黃人同班黑暴都咁老友 唔係要重燃抗爭之火咩<br />\n定係班黑暴比人拉曬 無人抗爭 革命啊 (下刪2千字...)<br />\n之後講完仲要係咁笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到我成個人都呆L曬 要諗諗點回撃<br />\n點知藍藍表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又繼續開火: 反正你地班小黃人都係自己圍爐<br />\n最中意就係喺連登做打手 自娛<br />\n咩天滅中共 咩咩係咪黃嘅<br />\n咩政府又出惡法<br />\n仲要自膠將光復香港 時代革命 打成革新香港 時代抗疫<br />\n唔知你地監底見緊嘅暴暴會有咩反應啊<br />\n<br />\n藍藍表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 真係笑死我 哈哈<br />\n仲學人講抗爭 革命<br />\n你地咪就係double thinking 緊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n依家線上等回覆中 有冇絲巴可以幫幫<br />\n大家睇下點回覆 <br />\n唔可以新年就比人滅我地黃人嘅威風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我依家去排隊拎初見嘅盤菜<br />\n用<span class=\"gold\"><strong>嘢食</strong></span>塞住佢把口先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1601f004664a7fdd39e916092ae25a8851570da","tid":2406432,"uid":384104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"小弟已經將母上封比藍藍表弟嘅利是 偷雞換咗做報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家請出招"},{"pid":"769ef315f771bd70a6179f222b89f681d9298c2d","tid":2406432,"uid":389214,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744336e1898daf8dcf9db3ebff93022d959ff7ab","tid":2406432,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote