大家請出招"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"10蚊啦，意思意思一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然最好係5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79595921be58c58147860e0a53b1c77907d39b1","tid":2406432,"uid":42687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"駛咩駁者，咪由佢囉，做人做到佢咁樣冇良知，到最後佢都係同自己交代架喳，佢覺得自己私隱DNA咁低賤咪由得佢。<br />\n利申：唔會再做傳道人"},{"pid":"ae2d1948a7dbee90ddd4fd4e52a7bd525c066c25","tid":2406432,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63c31ce5e6a4e0d38aa5881135354e3ad5ceb84","tid":2406432,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2d1948a7dbee90ddd4fd4e52a7bd525c066c25","tid":2406432,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"可愛絲 新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e3720b00a7e3236b2572a86f5396f203fd35c7","tid":2406432,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63c31ce5e6a4e0d38aa5881135354e3ad5ceb84","tid":2406432,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2d1948a7dbee90ddd4fd4e52a7bd525c066c25","tid":2406432,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets